rows.text: {{small|One-time [[NWA World Heavyweight Championship|NWA World Heavyweight Champion]], four-time [[TNA World Heavyweight Championship|TNA World Heavyweight Champion]] and one-time [[TNA World Tag Team Championship|TNA World Tag Team Champion]]}}

{{small|One-time [[IWGP Heavyweight Championship (IGF)|IWGP Heavyweight Champion]], six-time [[TNA World Heavyweight Championship|TNA World Heavyweight Champion]], one-time [[TNA X Division Champion]], two-time [[TNA World Tag Team Champion]] and two-time [[King of the Mountain match|King of the Mountain]] winner (2007, 2009)}}

{{small|Co-founder of TNA, one-time [[AAA Mega Championship|AAA World Heavyweight Champion]], six-time [[NWA World Heavyweight Championship|NWA World Heavyweight Champion]], one-time [[TNA King of the Mountain Championship|TNA King of the Mountain Champion]] and three-time [[King of the Mountain match|King of the Mountain]] winner (2004, 2006, 2015)}}

{{small|Inaugural and seven-time [[TNA Knockouts Championship|TNA Knockouts Champion]], one-time [[TNA Knockouts Tag Team Championship|TNA Knockouts Tag Team Champion]] and one-time [[Total Nonstop Action Wrestling tournaments#One Night Only|Queen of the Knockouts]] winner (2013)}}

{{small|One-time [[NWA World Heavyweight Championship|NWA World Heavyweight Champion]], two-time [[TNA Television Championship|TNA Television Champion]], one-time [[TNA X Division Championship|TNA X Division Champion]], two-time [[TNA World Tag Team Championship|TNA World Tag Team Champion]], one-time [[NWA World Tag Team Championship|NWA World Tag Team Champion]] and one-time [[Fight for the Right Tournament]] winner (2006)}}
